  <span id="freeText10261167103415483255" style="display:none">An exhilarating insight towards a mythical realm that is as much art as it is science. Awe-inspiring tales by a surgeon who wields his pen as he does his scalpel. A must read for every medical student, or anyone within the medical field. This book cemented my passion for surgery, and made my decision to be a surgeon a vivid one. It eradicated the notion I had about a profession centered around an innate talent and good manual dexterity; as I learned what it takes to be a surgeon is much more than that.</span>
